description: Create a stunning wall gallery in your home with this gorgeous set of 6-piece modern framed prints with unique individual designs. Each print is framed with a crisp white beveled mat and protective glass. Each frame has a wall footprint that measures 12.5 inches by 15.5 inches and is 1.5 inches deep, while the art print is 4.5 inches wide by 6.5 inches tall and the glass is 10.5 inches wide by 13.5 inches tall. A hanging template is included, which allows you to easily arrange a display of three frames across and two frames high making the approximate outer dimensions 40.4 inches across and 32.4 inches high. This eye-catching modern art set is the perfect addition to your modern home wall gallery.
